query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_properties,
  SUM(CASE WHEN primary_image IS NOT NULL AND primary_image != '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_primary_image,
  (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT property_id) FROM property_images) as properties_with_images
FROM properties;
